bin/
*.db
# .neurofs is local state (ledgers, caches, index) EXCEPT the tuned weight
# files: those are gate-validated engine tuning worth versioning — measured
# 2026-07-04, defaults vs tuned is 61% vs 89% search-surface recall. The
# `/*` form (not `/`) is required so the negations below can re-include.
**/.neurofs/*
!**/.neurofs/weights.json
!**/.neurofs/ranking_weights.json
*.prompt
*.env

.claude/
.DS_Store

audit/records/
audit/bundles/
audit/grounding.jsonl

/neurofs
